# Project Structure Guide

This document outlines the main structure of the Todo application codebase.

## Core Files
- [src/index.js](mdc:src/index.js) - Main entry point of the application
- [src/App.js](mdc:src/App.js) - Root component containing the main application logic
- [src/config.js](mdc:src/config.js) - Global configuration settings

## Key Directories
- `src/components/` - React components used throughout the application
- `src/context/` - React context providers for state management
- `src/hooks/` - Custom React hooks
- `src/services/` - API and external service integrations
- `src/utils/` - Utility functions and helper methods
- `src/config/` - Configuration files and constants

## Testing and Setup
- [src/setupTests.js](mdc:src/setupTests.js) - Test configuration
- [src/App.test.js](mdc:src/App.test.js) - Main application tests
- [src/reportWebVitals.js](mdc:src/reportWebVitals.js) - Performance monitoring

